text: Meisam Bagheri is an Iranian taekwondo athlete. He won a bronze medal at the 2009 World Taekwondo Championships in Copenhagen, Denmark, in the men's finweight. At the 2011 World Taekwondo Championships in Gyeongju, South Korea, he again won a bronze medal in the men's finweight. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Iranian male taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
